---
// 多行文本组件 - 用于批量 URL、日志备注和后续工具参数输入，统一校验状态和可访问性
import FormField from './FormField.astro';

const {
  id,
  name,
  label,
  hint,
  error,
  placeholder,
  value = '',
  required = false,
  disabled = false,
  readonly = false,
  rows = 5,
  maxlength,
  class: className = '',
  textareaClass = '',
  describedBy = '',
  ariaLabel,
  resize = 'vertical',
} = Astro.props;

const hintId = hint && id ? `${id}-hint` : '';
const errorId = error && id ? `${id}-error` : '';
const describedByValue = [describedBy, error ? errorId : hintId].filter(Boolean).join(' ') || undefined;
const textareaStateStyles = error
  ? 'border-red-400 focus:border-red-500 focus:ring-red-100'
  : 'border-orange-100 focus:border-violet-300 focus:ring-violet-100';
const resizeClass = resize === 'none' ? 'resize-none' : resize === 'both' ? 'resize' : 'resize-y';
---

<FormField id={id} label={label} hint={hint} error={error} required={required} class={className}>
  <textarea
    id={id}
    name={name}
    placeholder={placeholder}
    required={required}
    disabled={disabled}
    readonly={readonly}
    rows={rows}
    maxlength={maxlength}
    aria-label={ariaLabel}
    aria-invalid={error ? 'true' : undefined}
    aria-describedby={describedByValue}
    class={`min-h-[112px] w-full rounded-lg border bg-white px-4 py-3 text-[13px] font-semibold leading-relaxed text-gray-700 placeholder-gray-400 shadow-inner shadow-orange-50/70 transition-all duration-200 focus:outline-none focus:ring-4 disabled:cursor-not-allowed disabled:bg-gray-50 disabled:text-gray-400 ${resizeClass} ${textareaStateStyles} ${textareaClass}`}
  >{value}</textarea>
</FormField>
